🤖 Telegram Downloader Bot

A powerful Telegram bot to download videos, images, and media from links directly in Telegram.

🚀 Features

- 📥 Download videos & images from links
- ⚡ Fast processing
- 🔗 Supports multiple platforms
- 🤖 Easy Telegram commands

🛠 Requirements

- Python 3.x
- Telegram Bot Token (from @BotFather)

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

🔑 Setup Bot Token

1. Open Telegram and search @BotFather
2. Create a new bot using "/start" → "/newbot"
3. Copy your Bot Token

Now open "bot.py" and add your token:

TOKEN = "YOUR_BOT_TOKEN_HERE"

▶️ Run the Bot

python bot.py

📲 Commands

- "/start" → Start the bot
- "/help" → Show help message
- Send any media link → Bot will download it

📁 Output

Downloaded files are automatically sent back to the user in Telegram.

⚠️ Disclaimer

This bot is made for educational purposes only.
Do not use it to download copyrighted or illegal content.

